=Description=

"Introduction of José van Dijck at the World Interdisciplinary Network for Institutional Research (WINIR) conference as part of a roundtable "ICT, open societies and new institutions". 

José gives an interesting introduction on the platform economy and elaborates on the question: 'Do platforms bypass or replace institutions?'. 

Speakers on this roundtable: José van Dijck (Royal Netherlands Academy of Arts and Sciences), Haroon Sheikh (Dasym Investment Strategies) & Fredrik Söderqvist (Unionen)."


